&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://www.saravdv.be&#34; title=&#34;Sara Blogt... | There are no endings, only new beginnings&#34; rel=&#34;girlfriend muse contact met&#34;&gt;Sara&lt;/a&gt;, my girlfriend, regularly gets products to test and review for her blog. Off course as a photographer, I can&amp;rsquo;t resist the urge to use them to test out new techniques or ideas. So it happens that yesterday afternoon, I was standing in the living room, shooting Nespresso packshots with hot chocolate, milk and coffee.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Don&amp;rsquo;t forget, you can still subscribe for &lt;a href=&#34;http://pitslamp.com/blog/20130605_workshop-film-photography-and-darkroom&#34; title=&#34;Workshops film photography and darkroom&#34; rel=&#34;me&#34;&gt;the workshops film photography and darkroom&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

